div.p:
3. In my despatch 976, December 23rd,Not printed. the difficulties arising at Montevideo
                                between Paraguay and Bolivia are outlined, and mention was made that
                                the Foreign Office has in preparation an official note dealing with
                                these. This morning I received the note accompanied by copies of the
                                following official correspondence: 

First, memorandum Bolivian proposals;

Second, memorandum Paraguayan proposals;

Third, the Uruguayan formula;

Fourth, modifications requested by Bolivia;

Fifth, proposal offered by Paraguay;

Sixth, Bolivian refusal;

Seventh, new proposal by Paraguay.
